--- a/monorepo/CLAUDE.md	1970-01-01 01:00:00
+++ b/monorepo/CLAUDE.md	2025-12-28 12:01:26
@@ -0,0 +1,28 @@
+# {{package}}
+
+A Rust workspace with an embedded R package using miniextendr.
+
+## Build Commands
+
+```bash
+just check          # Run cargo check
+just rcmdinstall    # Build and install R package
+cargo fmt           # Format Rust code
+cargo clippy        # Run lints
+```
+
+## Architecture
+
+- `{{crate_name}}/` - Main Rust crate with core functionality
+- `rpkg/` - R package that exposes Rust functionality to R
+
+## Development Workflow
+
+For changes to fully propagate (especially macro changes), run these steps in order:
+
+```bash
+just configure          # 1. Vendor dependencies to rpkg/src/vendor/
+just rcmdinstall        # 2. Build and install R package
+just rdoc               # 3. Regenerate R wrappers and documentation
+just rcmdinstall        # 4. Rebuild with updated R wrappers
+```
